        {
            "_id": "MHNigTiEfg1SgrT0",
            "img": "systems/pf2e/icons/default-icons/action.svg",
            "name": "Reaction Reversal",
            "sort": 800000,
            "system": {
                "actionType": {
                    "value": "passive"
                },
                "actions": {
                    "value": null
                },
                "category": "offensive",
                "description": {
                    "value": "<p>Since an echopsyvne appears to move backwards in time and the results of its actions manifest slightly out of sync, its manipulate or move actions and Strikes don't trigger reactions normally. Whenever a reaction would be triggered by an echopsyvne in this way, the reacting creature must attempt a @Check[flat|dc:11]. On a failure, their reaction does not trigger.</p>"
                },
                "publication": {
                    "license": "OGL",
